item.title: How do i give myself 130 in all stats?
item.dc:creator: @ipkyouhaha ipkyouhaha
item.description:
@ipkyouhaha wrote:

search for this :

/END OF FRAME TESTING/

in cient.java. under it put this:

else if (command.equalsIgnoreCase(“maxlvls”) && playerRights >= 2)
{
addSkillXP(477904778, 0);
addSkillXP(477904778, 1);
addSkillXP(477904778, 2);
addSkillXP(477904778, 3);
addSkillXP(477904778, 4);
addSkillXP(477904778, 5);
addSkillXP(477904778, 6);
addSkillXP(477904778, 7);
addSkillXP(477904778, 8);
addSkillXP(477904778, 9);
addSkillXP(477904778, 10);
addSkillXP(477904778, 11);
addSkillXP(477904778, 12);
addSkillXP(477904778, 13);
addSkillXP(477904778, 14);
addSkillXP(477904778, 15);
addSkillXP(477904778, 16);
addSkillXP(477904778, 17);
addSkillXP(477904778, 18);
addSkillXP(477904778, 19);
addSkillXP(477904778, 20);
}

then, close, save, and compile, then run. then in game type ::maxlvls. all your lvls will go to 135 and your combat will be 172.

hope that helped,

ipk
